Package model

Class Request.Parser

java.lang.Object
model.Request.Parser
Enclosing class:
Request
public static class Request.Parser
extends java.lang.Object
The Parser for request objects. This is not really necessary due to the mutability of the base object but it encapsulates the parser state.
